@startuml 05-dependency-law
title Dependency Law — Each Layer's Allowed Ignorance

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "Canonical Facts\n(already admitted disorder)" as Facts
component "dteam process / globe math" as DTEAM
component "DTeamUnios trait\n(narrow operating contract)" as Trait
component "unios admission / proof" as UNIOS
component "unibit sealed substrate" as UNIBIT
component "Nightly Rust branchless kernels" as KERNEL
component "Pinned truth + scratch\n(UniverseBlock + UniverseScratch)" as REGION
component "ΔU + UReceipt" as PROOF
component "dteam verified result" as RESULT

Facts --> DTEAM
DTEAM --> Trait
Trait --> UNIOS
UNIOS --> UNIBIT
UNIBIT --> KERNEL
KERNEL --> REGION
REGION --> PROOF
PROOF --> RESULT

DTEAM ..> UNIBIT : does not import
DTEAM ..> KERNEL : does not import
DTEAM ..> REGION : does not import
UNIOS ..> KERNEL : does not know implementation of
UNIOS ..> REGION : does not address directly
RESULT ..> REGION : is not authority

note right of DTEAM
  Allowed fiction:
  input is canonical, punctual, complete.
  Imperfection is already an explicit fact.
end note

note right of UNIOS
  Allowed fiction:
  unibit API is truthful.
  Work executes per contract.
end note

note right of UNIBIT
  Allowed fiction:
  every handle received
  is already admitted.
end note

@enduml
